results.deck: Arkane Studios is a ZeniMax-owned game developer based in Lyon. They are best known for their 2002 RPG, Arx Fatalis.
results.description:
• On 07/10/2009 it was announced that they'd be helping out 2K Marin, 2K Australia and Digital Extremes with developing BioShock 2.
  • During QuakeCon '10, ZeniMax announced that they had acquired Arkane Studios. The studio has started working on an unannounced project, though no further details were made available.
  • On 07/07/2011 Bethesda announced that the title Arkane Studios are working on is called Dishonored. The title was described as having elements of stealth, a morality system and the ability to go through the entire game without killing anyone. Dishonored is developed for PlayStation 3, Xbox 360 and PC, and was released in October 2012.
